&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://spectrum.ge/images/Blog/9b09d4df249ced01f809f1e1b2bbe5a7.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With an emphasis on a clean, inviting atmosphere, the farmhouse style is defined by simplicity and some callbacks to years and styles went by.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In that way, it creates a timeless look. Last but not least, before you start your farmhouse remodel journey you need to choose if you prefer a traditional farmhouse (more similar to a country-style) or a modern farmhouse, that mixes country and modern elements achieving an overall more modern look.&lt;/p&gt;
